ActNational Defence Act
PrecisAppointment of TAMMY TREMBLAY of Ottawa, Ontario, who is not an officer or non-commissioned member of the Canadian Forces, nor an employee of the Department of National Defence, to be full-time Chairperson of the Military Police Complaints Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective January 3, 2023.
